label: TITLE
description: This field stores the person's title.

label: FIRST
description: This field stores the person's first name.

label: MIDDLE
description: This field stores the person's middle name.

label: LAST
description: This field stores the person's last name or the non-individual description.

label: SUFFIX
description: This field stores any suffix to the person's name.

label: LONGNAME
description: This field contains the computed long name of up to 40 characters that can be accessed with PowerOn for displays and reports

label: SHORTNAME
description: This field contains the computed short name of up to 16 characters to be used in displays and on reports.

label: EXTRAINFO
description: This field stores a line of miscellaneous information.

label: HEADQUARTERS
description: This field indicates if the record pertains to the entity's main base of operations or headquarters.

label: ADDRESSTYPE
description: This field stores a code that indicates whether the address should be in the U.S. Postal Service standard format or a foreign format.

label: EXTRAADDRESS
description: This field stores an extra address line.

label: STREET
description: This field stores the person's street address.

label: CITY
description: This field stores the person's city.

label: STATE
description: This field stores the person's state.

label: ZIPCODE
description: This field stores the person's city.

label: COUNTY
description: This field stores the county in which the person resides.

label: COUNTRY
description: This field stores the country in which the person resides.

label: COUNTRYCODE
description: This field stores the two-character country code where the person resides.

label: PHONETYPE
description: This field stores a code that indicates a domestic or foreign phone number type.

label: PREFERREDCONTACT
description: This field contains the preferred contact method.

label: HOMEPHONE
description: This field stores the person's home telephone number.

label: WORKPHONE
description: This field stores the person's work telephone number.

label: WORKPHONEEXTENSION
description: This field stores the person's telephone extension number at work.

label: MOBILEPHONE
description: This field stores the number for the person's cell phone or other mobile phone device (if any).

label: PAGERNUMBER
description: This field stores the number for the person's pager (if any).

label: EMAIL
description: This field stores the person's email address.

label: ALTEMAIL
description: This field stores the person's alternate email address.

label: PREFERREDCONTACTMETHOD
description: This field stores a code that indicates how the member wants to receive information from the credit union.

label: NAMEFORMAT
description: This field stores a code that indicates whether the name is an individual or not.

label: TYPE
description: This field stores a code that identifies the kind of Person record.

label: PERSONCODE
description: This field stores a code that indicates the relationship of this person to the application.

label: ACCOUNTNUMBER
description: This field stores the person's account number.

label: SSN
description: This field stores the person's account number.

label: RECORDCHANGEDATE
description: This field stores the system date in this field when you create, change, or save the Application Person record. Sometimes Symitar Quest updates this field because the record was saved, even though there may not be any actual changes in the record.

label: BIRTHDATE
description: This field stores the person's date of birth.

label: MARITALSTATUS
description: This field stores a code that indicates the person's marital status.

label: EDUCATIONYEARS
description: This field stores the total number of years of education the person has completed.

label: SEX
description: This field stores a code that indicates the person's sex.

label: CITIZENSHIP
description: This field stores a code that indicates whether the individual is a U.S. citizen.

label: MOTHERSMAIDENNAME
description: This field stores the maiden name of the person's mother.

label: OTHERCREDITNAME
description: This field stores any other name the person uses for credit accounts.

label: USPERSONFLAG
description: This field stores a code that specifies whether the person is a citizen of the United States, or whether the business identified is established or organized under the laws of a state or the United States.

label: LEI
description: This field stores the unique alpha-numeric code associated with a single corporate entity for international financial market record keeping.

label: BENEFICIALOWNER
description: This field stores a code that specifies whether the person directly or indirectly owns 25% or more of the equity interests or has significant responsibility to control, manage, or direct the legal entity customer.

label: BENEFICIALPERCENT
description: This field stores the percentage of the equity interests of the legal entity customer that this person owns.

label: ACTIVEDUTY
description: This field stores a code that identifies whether the borrower, or a family member, is in active military service.

label: ACTIVEDUTYVERIFICATIONDATE
description: This field stores the date when you verify that the borrower is on active duty or is the dependent of someone on active duty.

label: ACTIVEDUTYSTARTDATE
description: This field stores the date when the borrower begins active duty or is the dependent of someone who begins active duty.

label: ACTIVEDUTYSEPARATIONDATE
description: This field stores the date when the borrower is no longer on active duty or is the dependent of someone no longer on active duty.

label: IDENTDOCFLAG:1

label: IDENTIDTYPE:1

label: IDENTIDDESCRIPTION:1

label: IDENTIDNUMBER:1
description: This field stores the value of the type of identification specified by the corresponding ID type to support the first form of identification.

label: IDENTIDISSUEDATE:1
description: This field stores the date the type of identification specified by the corresponding ID type was issued, if known, to support the first form of identification.

label: IDENTIDEXPIREDATE:1
description: This field stores the date the type of identification specified by the corresponding ID type expires, if known, to support the first form of identification.

label: IDENTIDVERIFYDATE:1
description: This field stores the date the type of identification specified by the corresponding ID type was verified to support the first form of identification.
